{
  "text": "By manipulating a family of layer-structured materials to accommodate both ferroelectric and ferromagnetic cations within the same structure, we previously synthesized Aurivillius phase Bi6Ti2.8Fe1.52Mn0.68O18 by a chemical solution deposition (CSD) technique [CITATION_1] . This material is a multiferroic thin film material that demonstrates a ferromagnetic signature (MS = 0.74 emu/g, HC =",
